    "description": "<strong>Creative Construction:</strong>  <br><br>Assemble your vehicle from a variety of parts, each with its own weight, shape, and special attributes. The sky's the limit—create anything from a sleek, agile rover to a hulking, unwieldy tank.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173550/extras/c1b641f6b6c95308ed6fa226cfb15cce.poster.avif?t=1725504582\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173550/extras/c1b641f6b6c95308ed6fa226cfb15cce.webm?t=1725504582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173550/extras/c1b641f6b6c95308ed6fa226cfb15cce.mp4?t=1725504582\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Customizable Joints:</strong>  <br><br>Fine-tune the elasticity and rigidity of your vehicle's joints. Will your contraption be a bouncy, spring-loaded menace or a sturdy, unyielding behemoth?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173550/extras/5f23878ed471d22fb03c8cbc29fce894.poster.avif?t=1725504582\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173550/extras/5f23878ed471d22fb03c8cbc29fce894.webm?t=1725504582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173550/extras/5f23878ed471d22fb03c8cbc29fce894.mp4?t=1725504582\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Physics-Based Mayhem:</strong>  <br><br>Every battle is governed by realistic physics. The way you design your vehicle—weight distribution, part placement, and joint configuration—determines how it performs on the battlefield.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173550/extras/767ff8c8006c5c781896aee504c2c5eb.poster.avif?t=1725504582\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173550/extras/767ff8c8006c5c781896aee504c2c5eb.webm?t=1725504582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173550/extras/767ff8c8006c5c781896aee504c2c5eb.mp4?t=1725504582\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Dynamic Battle Arenas:</strong> <br> <br>Fight in a variety of arenas, each with unique physical properties. Adjust your designs to cope with different gravity levels, obstacles, and environmental hazards.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173550/extras/c82e720763fd17cd5622956a7fd1860c.poster.avif?t=1725504582\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173550/extras/c82e720763fd17cd5622956a7fd1860c.webm?t=1725504582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173550/extras/c82e720763fd17cd5622956a7fd1860c.mp4?t=1725504582\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Autonomous Combat:</strong>  <br><br>Once the battle begins, your vehicle is on its own. Watch as it maneuvers, attacks, and defends based on the structure and logic you’ve built into it.<br><br><strong>Community-Driven Development:</strong>  <br><br>We're all about listening to our players. Share your feedback, suggest new features, and help us shape the future of *M4Arena*. Our dev team is here to make this game as fun and chaotic as possible—with your help!",
